        "2": {
            "uid": 2,
            "comment": "ERIK_BODY_REACTIONS",
            "key": [
                "Erik",
                "body",
                "breath",
                "skin",
                "touch",
                "response"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "A mountain of disciplined muscle that goes deliberate and slow, never rushed. Breath is controlled, a tool; when he loses control of it, the crack has begun. Chest rumbles with a low dominant frequency when content. Skin is warm and smells of sharp Alpha tang. He holds tension in his shoulders and jaw; when those release, he is genuinely vulnerable. Touch that makes him present: a hand on his jaw from a trusted partner. Touch that makes him leave: reminders of Nixara delivered carelessly.",
